---
title: Golden Parmesan Chicken Schnitzels with Cherry Tomato Salad  & Smokey Aioli
description: It’s that time of the week, schnitty night! We’ve been looking forward to showing off this one. A sharp cheesy crumb coats tender chicken to transform it into the ultimate schnitzel. Add a dollop of smokey aioli for a flavourful finish.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 40g carbohydrates per serving.*

